skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: new york vegan
des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in New York. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable New York Vegan." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask New York Vegan for a fact."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
